                    <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Shipping costs depend on actual weight vs. volumetric (dimensional) weight. Carriers charge based on whichever is greater, making packaging optimization a key factor in reducing your freight costs. Understanding this rule helps you design packaging that minimizes shipping expenses without compromising product protection.</p>
